practitioner.about:
Dr. Zobaida Saloum is a Specialist in the Department of Obstetrics and Gynaecology at the Medcare Medical Centre. She obtained her MBBCh from Tishreen University in Latakia, Syria and an MD in Gynaecology & Obstetrics from the Syrian Board under the Ministry of Health, Damascus. She also holds a Diploma in Aesthetic Gynaecology from the American Aesthetic Association. She is a member of the American Association of Continuous Medical Education.

Dr. Saloum has worked in well-known hospitals and clinics across Syria and the UAE. She did her Residency in Obstetrics and Gynaecology at the National Hospital in Latakia, Syria and also worked at Al Othman Private Hospital in Syria before moving to the UAE. She served as a Specialist in Obstetrics and Gynaecology at IMC International Medical Center, the Saudi German Hospital and Prime Medical Center, all in Dubai. She worked with Seven Dimensions Medical Center LLC in Arjan before joining Medcare as a Specialist in Obstetrics and Gynaecology.

Having spent more than a decade in her area of specialization, Dr. Saloum’s range of expertise extends from pregnancy planning to delivery and all issues related to the health of the female reproductive system. She has proficiently managed complications related to normal and high-risk pregnancies, antenatal and postnatal care, adolescent health and puberty-related disorders, menopause, infertility and miscarriages. She performs cosmetic gynaecology and treats sexually transmitted diseases as well as polycystic ovarian disease.
In her spare time, she likes to catch up with her reading and likes to keep fit by playing sports. She speaks Arabic and English.

locations.about:
Medcare Medical Centre in Damac Hills stands as a premium, advanced healthcare facility devoted to meeting the diverse healthcare needs of its community. This inviting medical centre prioritizes comfort and convenience, providing cutting-edge facilities and comprehensive medical services all under one roof. Ideal for patients of every age seeking precise diagnoses and prompt treatment across various specialties.

 

At the helm of Medcare Medical Centre Damac Hills is a team of multicultural, multilingual doctors, complemented by exceptionally-trained and experienced nurses and medical staff. The centre takes pride in its extensive array of state-of-the-art equipment, empowering its highly skilled medical team to deliver a premium level of care to all patients. 

 

Experience the warmth of family-centric care delivered by our highly talented medical and non-medical staff. At Medcare Medical Centre Damac Hills, we offer a range of services, including Internal Medicine, Gynaecology, Paediatrics, Dermatology & Aesthetics, ENT, Dentistry, General Medicine, Orthopaedics & Physiotherapy and Radiology.

 

As part of our commitment to accessible healthcare, Medcare operates a network of four hospitals and 20 plus multi-specialty clinics across Dubai and Sharjah. Our goal is to provide reliable and timely medical care to our diverse clientele.

 

Great News! We are expanding to better suit all your medical and beauty needs!
